			description: ["Mine & Slash jewelry is equipped in Curios ring and necklace slots, providing powerful passive stat bonuses separate from armor. Each piece rolls random affixes from a family pool — offensive, defensive, or utility. Jewelry does not decay; invest in salvaging and rerolling for the best affixes."]
