			description: ["Tier 1 jewelry stat souls are your first step into Mine & Slash's jewelry system. Apply them to rings and necklaces to lock in a primary stat. Low tier souls carry modest bonuses but scale with your gear level — any jewelry is better than bare Curios slots."]
