		{
			description: ["Tier 6 jewelry souls represent the apex of Mine & Slash's jewelry system. Reserved for the highest-difficulty Atlas maps and endgame boss drops, these souls can define a character build entirely around a single piece. Do not waste them on unenchanted bases."]
