		{
			description: ["Curios adds dedicated equipment slots beyond the vanilla armor and hotbar: two ring slots and one necklace slot. Open the Curios inventory through your inventory screen — there is a button on the side that opens the Curios panel. Mine and Slash rings and necklaces go in these slots; they do not equip in the main four armor positions. Every Curios slot you leave empty is a stat budget you are not spending. Equip something in all three jewelry slots as soon as you have anything available."]
			id: "JW01000000000001"
