		{
			dependencies: ["JW01000000000001"]
			description: ["Two separate mods equip rings via the Curios ring slots, and they are not interchangeable systems. Soul Land soul rings — white, yellow, purple, black, red, and blue rank — are cultivation items that grant movement speed, qi cycling rate, and hold soul ring abilities absorbed from defeated Soul Beasts. They are part of the Soul Land progression and have nothing to do with Mine and Slash stats. Mine and Slash jewelry rings are gear pieces that roll affixes and use stat souls. You have two ring slots: filling both with MnS rings maximizes stat optimization; keeping a Soul Land ring equipped preserves its cultivation bonuses. Choose based on where you are in the game — Soul Land rings are early power, MnS rings are endgame optimization."]
			id: "JW01000000000002"
