			}]
			title: "Two Ring Systems"
			x: -3.0d
			y: -1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["JW01000000000002"]
			description: ["Unique jewelry pieces in Mine and Slash have fixed, predetermined affixes rather than random rolls. Where a Rare ring might give any combination of stats from its affix pool, a Unique ring has specific, non-random bonuses that define how it is used — often locked to a playstyle or build archetype. Unique jewelry is not craftable; it drops from endgame map bosses, Uber map completions, and specific high-tier mob kills. When a Unique drops, evaluate it against the specific bonuses it provides, not against a generic stat comparison. A well-matched Unique ring is often worth more than a perfectly-rolled Mythic random piece."]
			id: "JW01000000000003"
